channel.title: CVE Feed for Zoom Video Communications Inc -- Zoom (for Android, iOS, Linux, macOS, and Windows) clients before version 5.13.5
channel.description: The latest CVEs for Zoom Video Communications Inc -- Zoom (for Android, iOS, Linux, macOS, and Windows) clients before version 5.13.5

item.title: CVE-2023-22881|2024-08-02T10:20:31.192Z -- zoom%20video%20communications%20inc -- zoom%20%28for%20android%2C%20ios%2C%20linux%2C%20macos%2C%20and%20windows%29%20clients%20before%20version%205.13.5
item.description: Zoom clients before version 5.13.5 contain a STUN parsing vulnerability. A malicious actor could send specially crafted UDP traffic to a victim Zoom client to remotely cause the client to crash, causing a denial of service.
